584
00:30:02,341 --> 00:30:03,700
Miss Lv Zhu is simple-minded.

585
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:05,901
Stop your reckless fabrications.

586
00:30:06,821 --> 00:30:08,861
We're sorry. We won't do it again.

587
00:30:09,101 --> 00:30:10,301
