617
00:31:12,541 --> 00:31:14,141
Refund!

618
00:31:14,901 --> 00:31:15,660
We want refunds.

619
00:31:15,861 --> 00:31:17,061
- Open up!
- Open up!

620
00:31:17,660 --> 00:31:18,460
Open the door.

621
00:31:19,420 --> 00:31:19,940
Open the door.

