644
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:11,220
Refund!

645
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:12,901
Go follow that bearded man.

646
00:32:12,901 --> 00:32:13,740
Don't startle him.

647
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:14,740
See what he's up to.

648
00:32:14,740 --> 00:32:15,781
- We want refunds.
- Yes.

649
00:32:15,821 --> 00:32:17,180
(That person sneaked into the storeroom)

650
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:19,061
