take away the recipe?

654
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:29,500
I see.

655
00:32:29,500 --> 00:32:31,621
The recipe Laifu stole must be fake.

656
00:32:31,621 --> 00:32:32,581
The recipe was real.

657
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,500
Luo Xue'er is cunning.

658
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:35,980
