about Rose Liquor is the storage time.

664
00:32:51,420 --> 00:32:52,700
To Luo Xue'er,

665
00:32:52,700 --> 00:32:54,180
I'm an outsider to winemaking.

666
00:32:54,541 --> 00:32:57,180
She surely can't imagine
that I would retreat to advance

667
00:32:57,660 --> 00:32:58,660
and lay another trap.

668
00:32:59,020 --> 00:32:59,980
No wonder

669
00:33:00,541 --> 00:33:03,141
every time they make wine,
you will have the brewers

670
00:33:03,141 --> 00:33:04,141
leave for two hours

671
00:33:04,500 --> 00:33:06,260
