672
00:33:06,581 --> 00:33:09,141
You must have been
working on that crucial step.

673
00:33:09,740 --> 00:33:10,460
Exactly.

674
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:12,420
Although this recipe can brew

675
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,821
a wine that tastes
just like Rose Liquor,

676
