683
00:33:31,621 --> 00:33:34,341
Even if Luo Xue'er incurs losses,
they won't be too substantial.

684
00:33:34,861 --> 00:33:37,220
How did you figure
she would increase production?

685
00:33:37,581 --> 00:33:39,061
A fish swallows the hook for the bait.

686
00:33:39,781 --> 00:33:42,020
This recipe made Luo Xue'er a fortune.

687
00:33:43,260 --> 00:33:45,141
Money blinds.

688
00:33:46,101 --> 00:33:48,740
If a person's greed is unsatisfied,
and their intentions are evil,

689
00:33:49,301 --> 00:33:50,581
they are sure to reap what they sow.

690
00:33:51,581 --> 00:33:53,821
Plus, Luo Xue'er
is too eager to see me fail,

691
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:56,581
so I put on an act with my brother,

692
00:33:56,581 --> 00:33:57,740
pretending to make a comeback.

693
00:33:58,341 --> 00:33:59,861
She will therefore disregard everything.

694
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:03,980
By the time she realizes
something's wrong with the wine,

695
00:34:04,220 --> 00:34:05,541
it will already be too late.

696
00:34:05,781 --> 00:34:07,141
Miss, you are truly amazing.

697
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:10,420
You made her stock up a large amount
of ingredients to brew wine,

698
00:34:10,980 --> 00:34:13,060
and then you took advantage
of the rainy season

699
00:34:13,060 --> 00:34:14,620
to accelerate
the spoilage of Rose Drink.

700
00:34:15,020 --> 00:34:15,861
In this way,

701
00:34:15,980 --> 00:34:18,100
she has no choice but to lose all.

702
00:34:18,901 --> 00:34:19,701
However, Miss.

703
00:34:20,060 --> 00:34:21,500
I've been so worried,

704
00:34:21,861 --> 00:34:23,901
yet you didn't let on at all.

705
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:26,261
There can be no slip-ups
with this matter.

706
00:34:26,580 --> 00:34:28,500
So the fewer people knew, the better.

707
00:34:29,261 --> 00:34:31,861
I acted as if Luo Xue'er had enraged me

708
00:34:31,940 --> 00:34:33,221
to make her feel

709
00:34:33,221 --> 00:34:34,701
that we had no way out.

710
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:37,580
All of the Luo family's scheming

711
00:34:37,901 --> 00:34:39,781
was in your calculations.

712
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:41,741
And you countered her every move.

713
00:34:42,901 --> 00:34:43,980
It is truly brilliant.

714
00:34:44,661 --> 00:34:46,060
I am sincerely impressed.

715
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:48,460
Miss, your strategizing is ingenious.

716
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:49,741
There isn't a problem you can't solve.

717
00:34:50,980 --> 00:34:52,661
It's a rare lively day today.

718
00:34:53,221 --> 00:34:54,781
The lead in this farce

719
00:34:55,341 --> 00:34:56,741
is the best actress.

720
00:34:57,221 --> 00:34:58,620
How could we miss such a good play?

721
00:35:01,301 --> 00:35:01,940
Open the door.

722
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:02,741
Open the door.

723
00:35:07,181 --> 00:35:08,420
Hold it. Hold it.

724
00:35:09,301 --> 00:35:11,661
Shen Danqing must have
tampered with the recipe.

725
00:35:12,341 --> 00:35:13,861
So she set me up afterward.

726
00:35:14,301 --> 00:35:15,140
Miss Xue'er.

