00:35:42,861 --> 00:35:44,580
Ganlu Brewery has been
in Liao City for long.

739
00:35:44,781 --> 00:35:46,261
We will not betray everyone's trust.

740
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:48,741
I will definitely refund everyone.

741
00:35:48,901 --> 00:35:50,460
Tell us when you will refund the money.

742
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:51,940
Yes, tell us when.

743
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:53,580
Refund!

744
00:35:53,580 --> 00:35:54,580
Everyone, please be patient.

745
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,301
You can follow Laifu

746
00:35:56,460 --> 00:35:57,701
to register the refund amount.

747
00:35:58,100 --> 00:35:59,301
Give us three days.

748
00:35:59,460 --> 00:36:01,701
In three days, I will surely
have the money prepared

749
00:36:01,741 --> 00:36:03,821
and wait for you
in the main hall of Ganlu Brewery.

750
00:36:04,100 --> 00:36:05,500
